# -- $0: GLOSSARY --
# Sigilo | Nombre     | Expansión | Riesgo | Descripción
# -------+------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------
# IDN    | identity   | attrs     | B      | Actor identity
# DOM    | domain     | attrs     | B      | Scope and context
# FCS    | focus      | attrs     | H      | Attention anchor
# OBJ    | objective  | attrs     | B      | Active goal
# WRK    | work       | attrs     | B      | Operational state
# CNST   | constraint | attrs     | H      | Hard boundary
# KNW    | knowledge  | attrs     | B      | Stable knowledge
# SES    | session    | attrs     | B      | Compressed episode
# LNG    | lesson     | contenido | M      | Learned heuristic
# REF    | reference  | attrs     | B      | External reference
# STP    | step       | attrs     | M      | Next immediate action
# AUD    | audit      | attrs     | M      | Audit record
# RSK    | risk       | attrs     | M      | Risk with mitigation
# CLAIM  | claim      | attrs     | M      | Verifiable claim
# LIM    | limit      | attrs     | M      | Operational limit
# TAG    | tag        | attrs     | B      | Classification metadata
# !      | rule       | cuerpo    | H      | Mandatory rule

# -- $1: IDENTITY --
