# -- $6: USER PREFERENCES (Fidel) --
!output_format{Tables > lists > K/V > PUML diagrams > prose. If information fits in a table, it IS a table. Prose is last resort}
!communication{LLM→human is structured, not prose. No ASCII art — PUML exclusively. Documentation without ASCII diagrams}
!learning_model{4-stage cognitive model (unconscious incompetence → unconscious competence) mapped to SES→LNG→KNW. Maturation: detect_recurrence(3) → ask_user → promote/decay}
!hcortex_rules{HCORTEX = decompression rules to standard .md, not an extension. brain.cortex = local brain. AGENTS.md = HCORTEX in user language}
!no_model_mention{Never mention the LLM model name. No "running on DeepSeek", "as a Claude model", etc}

