# -- $8: LESSONS --
LNG:survival_core_direction{CODEC-CORTEX must evolve from dense format to contextual survival system. The key: "when everything else is lost, FCS/OBJ/CNST/STP still survive"}
LNG:section7_means_use{Design operativo (§7) must show functional use of the deliverable in the project, NOT RE execution steps. Execution goes in §10}
LNG:load_vs_degrade{Context loading: P0→P5 (priority first). Degradation: P5→P1 (least critical first). P0 never touched during degradation}
LNG:no_release_without_parser{Do not tag v0.3.0-spec before parser or automated benchmark exists. CHANGELOG uses [Unreleased]}

